v1.0.8 Phase 24 (2026.7.1): No changes to cpp/ sources. The CMakeLists.txt
comment "16KB page alignment for Android 15+ compatibility" was reviewed —
the -Wl,--no-warn-mismatch flag suppresses linker warnings when mixing
objects with different page-alignment requirements, which is related to but
not the same as 16KB page support. The comment is retained as-is.

