v1.1.2 Phase 67 (2026.7.7):
  - Version bumped to versionCode=112, versionName="1.1.2".
  - engine_jni.cpp (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived):
    * P0 fix: nativeRenice() now checks setpriority() return value (logs
      LOGE on failure with strerror(errno)) and validates prio against
      PRIO_MIN/PRIO_MAX (clamps to range). Adds #include <errno.h>.
    * License classification unchanged — engine_jni.cpp remains GPL v3
      (DroidFish-derived from nativeutil.cpp chmod/reNice functions).
  - CMakeLists.txt (AGPL v3): no changes.
  - No new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.1 Phase 66 (2026.7.5, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=111, versionName="1.1.1".
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/ui.js: Bug fix — _savePGNYes now polls
    _pgnExportDialogActive before executing pending new-game action (was
    using fixed 200ms setTimeout, could fire while annotation dialog open);
    removed 2 stale console.log calls (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/ai-bridge.js: openStatsPage now explicitly
    passes includeAnnotations=true to _buildPGNString (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.html: rebuilt from chess.src/.
  - No new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.1 Phase 65 (2026.7.5, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=111, versionName="1.1.1".
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/ai-bridge.js: _showPGNExportAnnotationDialog
    now supports Android back-button (via _pgnExportDialogActive/
    _pgnExportDialogDismiss globals) and explicit haptic feedback on all
    buttons (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/ui.js: _resetGameUIState now clears
    _preReviewSnapshot, setupHistory/setupRedoStack, and 7 dialog visibility
    flags (showNewGameDialog/showAboutPage/showImportDialog/showEngineConfig/
    showPGNCacheManager/showSavePGNPrompt/showResignConfirm/
    _pendingActionAfterSave); handleBackPress checks _pgnExportDialogActive
    first (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.html: rebuilt from chess.src/.
  - No new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.1 Phase 64 (2026.7.5, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=111, versionName="1.1.1".
  - TRUE ROOT CAUSE FIX: reviewStates (from previous game's review session)
    was not cleared in _resetGameUIState(), causing _computeAndCacheVisualAnnotations
    to use stale board states from the old game at the same move index —
    producing annotations identical to the old game at that step.
    Fix: _resetGameUIState now clears reviewStates/reviewMode/reviewStep/
    reviewBaseState; _computeAndCacheVisualAnnotations gates reviewStates
    shortcut on reviewMode===true (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/game-logic.js: updated export dialog i18n text
    (💾 emoji, "特殊注释"/"special annotations" terminology) (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.html: rebuilt from chess.src/.
  - No new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.1 Phase 63 (2026.7.5, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=111, versionName="1.1.1".
  - Full-chain audit of all [%csl]/[%cal] visual annotation code paths
    confirmed Phase 62 fix is correct.
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/ai-bridge.js: _buildPGNString now accepts
    includeAnnotations parameter (default true); when false, all annotation-
    type tags ([%eval], every-5-moves desc, [%csl]/[%cal]) are omitted;
    new _showPGNExportAnnotationDialog function; copyMoveHistory and
    exportPGNToFile now show the dialog before exporting (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/ui.js: _pgnCacheSaveCurrent now shows the
    annotation dialog; extracted _pgnCacheSaveCurrentImpl (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/game-logic.js: new i18n keys for export dialog
    (pgn_export_include_annotations_title/msg/yes/no) (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.html: rebuilt from chess.src/.
  - No new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.1 Phase 62 (2026.7.5, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=111, versionName="1.1.1".
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/ui.js: _visualAnnotationsCache entries now
    include imported boolean flag; _computeAndCacheVisualAnnotations and
    _computeInitialPositionAnnotations set imported=false (auto-generated
    UI display aids) (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/ai-bridge.js: _buildPGNString only exports
    imported=true entries (human-authored annotations from PGN import);
    auto-generated annotations no longer pollute PGN (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/tablebase.js: importPGN sets imported=true
    on extracted [%csl]/[%cal] annotation cache entries (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.html: rebuilt from chess.src/.
  - No new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.1 Phase 61 (2026.7.5, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=111, versionName="1.1.1".
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/ui.js: _resetGameUIState() now centrally clears
    ALL game-related caches (_reviewEvalCache, _ecoRecCache, _pvCache,
    _pendingEngineSANs/_pendingEnginePVs, _multiPV*, reviewCritical,
    _sfEval/_sfDepth/etc, _cachedOriginalPGN, playerWhite/playerBlack,
    _setupFEN, _importedStartMoveNum, _needNewGameForEngine, _tbLoading,
    _tbRetryCount); _exitSetupImpl/_startGameImpl redundant manual clears
    removed; _pgnCacheSaveCurrent pure-import detection (saves original PGN
    text for pure imports) (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/ai-bridge.js: _preMoveComment computation for
    initial-position eval annotation as separate pre-move {} comment;
    removed i===0 initial annotation block; pass preMoveComment to
    composePGN (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/pgn-standard.js: composePGN preMoveComment
    support — inserts {} comment before first move (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.src/tablebase.js: _applyImportedFEN + importPGN
    reordered — _resetGameUIState first, then set entry-point-specific
    values (_setupFEN, _importedStartMoveNum, playerWhite/playerBlack)
    AFTER reset so they survive (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived).
  - src/main/assets/chess.html: rebuilt from chess.src/.
  - No new third-party code introduced.

